snippet: Former Virginia governor Robert McDonnell and his wife were indicted on Tuesday by a federal grand jury and charged with accepting bribes in the form of money and gifts from the chief executive of a dietary supplements maker....

headline.print_headline: Ex-Governor of Virginia Indicted on Bribery Charges
headline.main: Ex-Governor of Virginia Indicted on Bribery Charges

lead_paragraph: Former Virginia governor Robert McDonnell and his wife were indicted on Tuesday by a federal grand jury and charged with accepting bribes in the form of money and gifts from the chief executive of a dietary supplements maker.
